{"tid":1109211,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知乜野數學題 求解！！！","createTime":"2019-04-16T08:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T05:21:24.000Z","uid":248664,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8394f15386cb31862c2554cda9086d3b92917b","tid":1109211,"uid":248664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:18:39.000Z","msg":"某公司倉庫有萬字夾（以盒計）<br />\na部門取了一半再加半盒，b部門取了一半再加半盒，c部門取了最後的一半再加半盒，清空了倉庫，請問最少要有幾多盒萬字夾？"},{"pid":"7995d918d274dc5959bbb6cb26a848cd72c9167e","tid":1109211,"uid":248664,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:22:28.000Z","msg":"求解答 我就計到7 但係唔知準唔準 <br />\nA: 7/2 + 0.5 =4<br />\nB: 3/2 +0.5 =2 <br />\nC: 0.5+0.5=1"},{"pid":"cbd9e17145afeed478db668da804c587afeaea06","tid":1109211,"uid":3675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"五盒"},{"pid":"2029b2af42e90bfc3d351b8f032a3fa96af817e2","tid":1109211,"uid":248664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbd9e17145afeed478db668da804c587afeaea06","tid":1109211,"uid":3675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"五盒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:29:28.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05b9f45b17db43167af40d3788e36e1af8c604d","tid":1109211,"uid":62532,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ea8394f15386cb31862c2554cda9086d3b92917b","tid":1109211,"uid":248664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:18:39.000Z","msg":"某公司倉庫有萬字夾（以盒計）<br />\na部門取了一半再加半盒，b部門取了一半再加半盒，c部門取了最後的一半再加半盒，清空了倉庫，請問最少要有幾多盒萬字夾？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"total = x<br />\nA : x - 0.5x - 0.5 = y<br />\nB : y - 0.5y - 0.5 = z<br />\nC : z - 0.5z - 0.5 =0<br />\nso<br />\nz = 1<br />\ny = 3<br />\nx = 7"},{"pid":"cf946ea481b032e475be49148f19acc3fd4f72b9","tid":1109211,"uid":100661,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:36:12.000Z","msg":"取一半 = 一定係成盒計？<br />\n3盒拎一半係點計？<br />\n照計半盒？"},{"pid":"e6b86f4989cf38e10eedd74dc0d2294b41fcad20","tid":1109211,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"LET 最少要有X盒萬字夾<br />\nA拿了萬字夾後 剩返(X/2 - 0.5)盒, let it as A'<br />\nB拿了萬字夾後 剩返(A'/2 - 0.5)盒, let it as B'<br />\nC拿了萬字夾後 剩返(B'/2 - 0.5)盒, let it as C'<br />\nC' = 0<br />\n<br />\nsub A' in B', then sub B' into C'<br />\nC' = ((X/2 - 0.5)/2 - 0.5)/2 - 0.5 = 0<br />\n((X/2 - 0.5)/2 - 0.5)/2 = 0.5<br />\n(X/2 - 0.5)/2 - 0.5 = 1<br />\n(X/2 - 0.5)/2 = 1.5<br />\nX/2 - 0.5 = 3<br />\nX/2 = 3.5<br />\nX=7"},{"pid":"f05b0f487209352c1f8b9af82da51e7d02325bf0","tid":1109211,"uid":248664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f05b9f45b17db43167af40d3788e36e1af8c604d","tid":1109211,"uid":62532,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ea8394f15386cb31862c2554cda9086d3b92917b","tid":1109211,"uid":248664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:18:39.000Z","msg":"某公司倉庫有萬字夾（以盒計）<br />\na部門取了一半再加半盒，b部門取了一半再加半盒，c部門取了最後的一半再加半盒，清空了倉庫，請問最少要有幾多盒萬字夾？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"total = x<br />\nA : x - 0.5x - 0.5 = y<br />\nB : y - 0.5y - 0.5 = z<br />\nC : z - 0.5z - 0.5 =0<br />\nso<br />\nz = 1<br />\ny = 3<br />\nx = 7"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:41:56.000Z","msg":"Ching 好波!!! 我都計到係7 不過唔肯定~~~"},{"pid":"48447487593cf3c190f567cff969d9de254e4839","tid":1109211,"uid":248664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cf946ea481b032e475be49148f19acc3fd4f72b9","tid":1109211,"uid":100661,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:36:12.000Z","msg":"取一半 = 一定係成盒計？<br />\n3盒拎一半係點計？<br />\n照計半盒？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:42:43.000Z","msg":"姐係全部既一半再加多半盒"},{"pid":"39a558c563c6957b62f6756f030f0b81227b6d10","tid":1109211,"uid":248664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6b86f4989cf38e10eedd74dc0d2294b41fcad20","tid":1109211,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"LET 最少要有X盒萬字夾<br />\nA拿了萬字夾後 剩返(X/2 - 0.5)盒, let it as A'<br />\nB拿了萬字夾後 剩返(A'/2 - 0.5)盒, let it as B'<br />\nC拿了萬字夾後 剩返(B'/2 - 0.5)盒, let it as C'<br />\nC' = 0<br />\n<br />\nsub A' in B', then sub B' into C'<br />\nC' = ((X/2 - 0.5)/2 - 0.5)/2 - 0.5 = 0<br />\n((X/2 - 0.5)/2 - 0.5)/2 = 0.5<br />\n(X/2 - 0.5)/2 - 0.5 = 1<br />\n(X/2 - 0.5)/2 = 1.5<br />\nX/2 - 0.5 = 3<br />\nX/2 = 3.5<br />\nX=7"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e80cdf69e5b3159b51e224bb4d1d07254d99e28","tid":1109211,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:48:44.000Z","msg":"((0.5*2+0.5)*2+0.5)*2=7"},{"pid":"4fb4b1d9d0197af8942037a0f6631ac2a04dad90","tid":1109211,"uid":26887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"想問點解最後加左半盒會清空咗，唔係應該仲有半盒咩"},{"pid":"0a4f24a156fc9009d5e36c7148635233b47c6b80","tid":1109211,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:54:34.000Z","msg":"反而想問最少要有7盒 咁最多可以有幾多盒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f69cfd57b29c348927ad14164de123c82e1c61f","tid":1109211,"uid":241357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"岩岩教完奧數就係教呢課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8faf9de46a06f2ac275e84eaffb2e6cc0947312","tid":1109211,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4fb4b1d9d0197af8942037a0f6631ac2a04dad90","tid":1109211,"uid":26887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"想問點解最後加左半盒會清空咗，唔係應該仲